{"tid":1233633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【學術討論】夜晚衝既Cost & Benefit Analysis","createTime":"2019-06-16T20:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T20:06:51.000Z","uid":258197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b9820ae42c2ac4314131fb651bd150d81dd1c15d","tid":1233633,"uid":258197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學術討論，剩係講夜晚衝既行為：<br />\nCost<br />\n&mdash;遊行左成日都攰<br />\n&mdash;無支援（人／物／記者）<br />\n&mdash;壞印象（？）＆敵方借勢出動＋洗白<br />\n（對方只會放大衝突並縮小遊行造成既壓力，到時就算唔係鬼但都造成派鬼入黎既效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n&mdash;對方呀頭指出唔係開緊會主動做乜<br />\n&mdash;諗返每次夜晚先係最危險既時間<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦都唔好做無謂行為：燒野既目的係咩先？如果係阻礙對面過黎，諗諗係咪無其他方案？或者有咩原因說服到大家係到左非燒不可既地步先<br />\n要知道有D野一做，個後果可能會好大，自己分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBenefit <br />\n&mdash;設防可以增加撤退時間<br />\n&mdash;好似諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勇武同和理非係互補關係而唔係替代關係，自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「兄弟爬山，各自努力」，唔好剩係將個重點放係後半句，有D野一做，你害左你兄弟。<br />\n唔好成日剩係拎依句出黎，咁大個人自己分析時勢情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：Econ 拎U<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704ea0facf2cc5b6ed08653e3e06f8e3b23313fc","tid":1233633,"uid":143210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:01:35.000Z","msg":"延伸<br />\n<br />\n而家係和理非嘅回合！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唱歌嘅時候就係夜晚<br />\n<br />\n衝嘅時候就係日頭"},{"pid":"1de22c15fd2625086361d636dbcec5543edb9cc3","tid":1233633,"uid":1139,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:01:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c80ebc1bf301c3828bda026257f2eb46c1298de","tid":1233633,"uid":12557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:02:35.000Z","msg":"[重要必睇]如何防止今次抗爭變成雨傘2.0, 魚革2.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233554</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"89f9aaa1af3c7fd85d5868bc118644d9ec5c8eb0","tid":1233633,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:03:10.000Z","msg":"benefit<br />\n- 夜闌人靜冇人阻你<del>做傻事</del>"},{"pid":"5b0f96c43ca1bf6c63953bd284af5095e55a83f7","tid":1233633,"uid":258197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"704ea0facf2cc5b6ed08653e3e06f8e3b23313fc","tid":1233633,"uid":143210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:01:35.000Z","msg":"延伸<br />\n<br />\n而家係和理非嘅回合！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唱歌嘅時候就係夜晚<br />\n<br />\n衝嘅時候就係日頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:04:16.000Z","msg":"Ａgger 唱歌既時候係夜晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2eb2ea7f8ff031bc1f5d89f8f3cd39ddc2edc4","tid":1233633,"uid":258197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:06:51.000Z","msg":"btw另一個考慮既點係日頭多d記者映到野助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}